{
	precache
	"num_pages"	: "2"
	"page1_left_title"	:
	{
		"03/02"
	}
	"page1_left_body"	:
	{
		""
		""
		"...arrived at the inn tonight.  Not a bad place really, just needs a bit of a work.  Certainly not the dive I was expecting."
		""
		"The innkeeper got a bit funny though when I asked how business was going."
	}
	"page1_right_title"	:
	{
		"05/02"
	}
	"page1_right_body"	:
	{
		""
		""
		"According to the locals, half this town is owned by 'Lord' Twistletoe, although the provenance of that title is suspect.  He apparently showed up about a year ago and started buying up property, starting with his house across the street."
	}
	"page2_left_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_left_body"	:
	{
		"Either way I'm going to see what else I can turn up.  Between the twtichy inkeeper and this dodgy Twistletoe something is going on."
	}
	"page2_right_title"	:
	{
		""
	}
	"page2_right_body"	:
	{
		""
	}
